title: Dead Bang  (MKV)
description:
R | 1h 42min | Action, Crime, Drama | March 24th 1989




A cop is gunned down on Xmas eve. Jerry Beck, the homicide cop given the job of hunting the killer, investigates some leads which bring him into contact with a group of white supremacy extremists.



Director: John Frankenheimer

Writers: Robert Foster (screenplay), Jerry Beck (story)

Stars: Don Johnson, Penelope Ann Miller, William Forsythe


English and French audio
